Home is where you feel protected.


YOU COULD SAVE AN AVERAGE OF $325 WHEN YOU SWITCH TO TRAVELERS HOME INSURANCE.







Explore Our Discounts



Multi-Policy Discount - You can save up to 15% on home insurance when you also purchase your auto insurance with Travelers.
Protective Device Discounts - Provides a variety of ways to save by having devices such as, smoke detectors and alarms, interior sprinkler systems, and home security systems such as deadbolts, alarms and 24-hour security guard.
Home Buyer Discount - Available to customers who have purchased their home within the prior 12 months to the policy effective date.
Loss-Free Discount - Offered to eligible customers who have not experienced a loss.
Green Home Discount - You could save up to 5% if your home is certified "green" by the Leadership Energy & Environmental Design organization.




What's Covered



Damage to your home's physical structure
Damage to other structures like a garage or shed
Damage to your personal belongings - whether in your home or elsewhere
Additional living expenses if necessary in the event of a covered loss
Your personal liability in the event someone is injured or their property is damaged by you or a family member




Fast Claim Service



Fast, efficient claim service and 24/7 claim reporting
Skilled claim professionals located throughout the country to respond quickly to both routine and catastrophic claims
Highly trained claim professionals available to inspect your property or auto if you experience a covered loss
Catastrophe response teams that can quickly mobilize to respond to a severe weather event











