Home/Agents / Brokers




BenefitsBecome An Agent


A.M. Best Rating
A.M. Best Has Affirmed the A++ (Superior) Ratings of Berkshire Hathaway Homestate Companies and Its Affiliates
Read More





Financial strength, ease of doing business and a relationship you’ll value are all reasons to choose BHHC. While our A.M. Best financial strength rating of A++ Superior (as of June 17, 2014) will give you the confidence to know BHHC will be here for years to come, it’s our effort to go the extra mile, as well as our personal service, that you’ll remember.   BHHC strives to exceed your expectations by tailoring service plans, delivering fast underwriting response times, offering easy access to policy information and providing high levels of service in claims, client services, loss control, premium audit and underwriting. Additionally, BHHC provides a local marketing resource to be there when you need them.
So why wait? Complete our Prospective Agency Application today.





