Home/Commercial Auto




Product InformationTruckingPublic AutoAll OtherCoveragesAuto Rater InformationReport a ClaimResources



With our A++ (Superior) financial strength rating from A.M. Best (as of June 2015), BHHC maintains its position as a consistent carrier through the commercial auto market's unpredictable swings. We offer a breadth of classes, unparalleled by other standard commercial auto insurance companies. Whether your business has one vehicle or a large fleet, we possess the knowledge and experience necessary to cater to the uniqueness of your company.   
Highlights of our Commercial Auto product:

Extensive product offering
Fast quote turnaround
Competitive commissions
Online rating capabilities
Direct Bill options featuring continuous renewal billing plan
Credit Card or EFT payments available

