Attention! Interview Scam
Please be advised that BHHC does not conduct interviews via social media (e.g., via Google hangouts, LinkedIn, etc.). Please be aware that any such contact or interview conducted in this manner is fraudulent and we advise that you not provide any personal information. Please report suspicious recruiting activity to recruiting-wc@bhhc.com.






With office locations throughout the United States, BHHC offers many career opportunities.  The variety of courses of study we consider and positions available might surprise you.  We hire both entry level and experienced employees with diverse professional and educational resumes.  From an internship in accounting to a career as a divisional vice president, BHHC has an opportunity for you.

