A.M. Best Rating
A.M. Best Has Affirmed the A++ (Superior) Ratings of Berkshire Hathaway Homestate Companies and Its Affiliates
Read More




Customer Care Center
Contact our Customer Care Center at(888) 495-8949.






BHHC is a workers compensation specialist with expertise in creating a better quality experience for our policyholders. This encompasses everything from compassionate care for injured workers to an improved financial position through state-of-the-art accident prevention techniques, return-to-work programs, and effective fraud mitigation.
Our parent company, Berkshire Hathaway, is on Fortune’s list of Most Admired companies for the second year in a row, and is listed 1st in the Property & Casualty Industry. Read more about our ranking.
Financial Strength
A.M. Best affirmed its highest A++ (Superior) financial strength rating for all six of our member Berkshire Hathaway Homestate Companies. Additionally, the ratings outlook for each of our BHHC member companies is stable. Our prudent efforts have not only yielded a track record of consistently high ratings, they have also enabled us to offer coverage for a wide variety of Workers Compensation risks under all market conditions. Disciplined risk selection and pricing ensure that we can capably write a diverse array of businesses spanning size, geography, type of work, and previous claims experience.
Compassionate Care
We are dedicated to helping injured workers achieve the fullest possible medical recovery through effective and timely treatment and support. We offer 24/7 access for new claim reporting via toll-free phone and fax lines, as well as an online tool, and we place great importance on our ability to contact the injured worker and you as quickly as possible. We have partnered with preferred provider networks across the country to ensure the highest quality care, and our claims professionals have low, manageable caseloads. This enables us to put our focus where it belongs: creating optimal outcomes for injured workers.
"BHHC's knowledge and enthusiasm has really helped improve our safety program."
Broad Appetite
Our Underwriters look at the merits of your individual business – not just your type of business. This allows us to not only offer coverage to a greater variety of customers at the outset, but it also enables us to grow with you as your business evolves over time.
National Reach
We are in all 46 states that allow insurance carriers to compete in providing workers compensation insurance. Our Underwriters have the authority to handle all the states in which your business operates. You get one Underwriter devoted to your entire business.
Exceptional Service
We believe responsiveness is the key to effective communication. Whether you have questions about billing, policy changes, or claims, you deserve answers and assistance when – and how - you need them. We pride ourselves on offering quality Claims, Premium Audit, and Loss Control services. 
Available States:
Click each state for contact information.








