Protection and Coverage –Far and Wide





Home/Public Entity




CoveragesReport a Claim



The BHHC Public Entity product provides coverage for cities, counties and villages in select Midwestern states. Designed for small to medium-sized communities, our product combines the financial strength of BHHC with more than 30 years of public-sector underwriting experience. By providing tailored coverage forms, specialized loss control services, and responsive claims handling, BHHC’s Public Entity product provides our agency partners a strong option for this unique niche of the commercial insurance market.
The BHHC Public Entity target market:

Municipalities (up to 25,000 population)
Counties (up to 40,000 population)
Villages
Non-metropolitan locales

For answers to any of your Public Entity questions, contact us at:
P: (800) 488.2930 publicentity@bhhc.com
Available States:
Click each state for contact information.



