A Broad Appetite for Commercial Auto 





Home/Commercial Auto/Product Information




Product InformationTruckingPublic AutoAll OtherCoveragesAuto Rater InformationReport a ClaimResources



BHHC offers a versatile monoline Commercial Auto product that targets local to long-haul trucks, public auto transportation and many other auto classes, such as non-emergency medical transportation, charter buses and tow trucks. 
Highlights of our Commercial Auto product:

New ventures welcome
No radius or unit count restrictions
High policy limits (up to $5,000,000)
Cargo limits (up to $500,000)
Loss-free credit available
Any application form accepted
Additional coverages available 






